@startuml
title WP3B-12: As an Administrator, I want to generate monthly reports showing total appointments, cancellations, and reschedules.

actor Administrator
control AppointmentController
control AppointmentService
entity AppointmentRepository

Administrator -> AppointmentController : GET /api/appointments/monthly-report
AppointmentController -> AppointmentService : getMonthlyReport()
AppointmentService -> AppointmentRepository : findAll()
AppointmentRepository --> AppointmentService : List<Appointment>
AppointmentService --> AppointmentController : List<MonthlyAppointmentReport>
AppointmentController --> Administrator : 200 OK (List<Report per Month>)

@enduml
